                            <comment id="101150" author="adilger" created="Tue, 9 Dec 2014 21:06:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Nathaniel, it looks like this may be the last major blocker for enforcing review-zfs.  Any chance to get a patch for this quickly?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="101099" author="utopiabound" created="Tue, 9 Dec 2014 16:42:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It still seems to fail on ZFS, though test 84 passed in local testing, but I didn&apos;t run full conf-sanity, I just ran test_84.  I think it&apos;s expecting a setup it&apos;s not getting for ZFS because of skipped test 83.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
