                            <comment id="100942" author="utopiabound" created="Mon, 8 Dec 2014 15:47:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4119&quot; title=&quot;recovery time hard doesn&amp;#39;t limit recovery duration&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4119&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4119&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch added a second test_83.&lt;/p&gt;

